UserComments.Comment: Waitrose have now imposed a strict customers only rule on these charging points. You will be required to spend £20 in store in order to charge.

Waitrose normally charge for parking unless you spend £20 in store. The parking attendant was very helpful and allowed me to charge for 4 hours free of charge. Drive up the car park ramp to find charge points on the 1st level.

UsageCost: Inclusive; for Polar Plus subscription members only

AddressInfo.Title: Waitrose Fulham
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Located at the top of the ramp on the 1st level of the car park. Inform parking attendant before use to avoid high parking charges.

GeneralComments: Chargemaster post. Polar Network cards accepted, but no longer accepts Source London
